.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-CREATE-OFFER" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-create-offer \- create a BOLT 12 offer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-create-offer
.IR amount_msat | any
.RI [ description ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates a reusable BOLT 12 offer via
.BR offer .
Use
.B any
as the amount for open-amount offers.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice (1),
.BR lightning-node-offers-list (1)
